(6215, 309, 'our_process_1_processname', 'Pre-Production Planning & Logistics'),
(6216, 309, '_our_process_1_processname', 'field_67c7d07b89280'),
(6217, 309, 'our_process_1_picon', ''),
(6218, 309, '_our_process_1_picon', 'field_67c7d09189281'),
(6219, 309, 'our_process_1_pcontent', 'With a clear concept in place, we meticulously plan every detail of the production. This includes location scouting, casting, scheduling, crew coordination, and budget management.  We handle all the logistics so you can focus on the creative aspects.'),
(6220, 309, '_our_process_1_pcontent', 'field_67c7d09b89282'),
(6221, 309, 'our_process_2_processname', 'Filming & Production'),
(6222, 309, '_our_process_2_processname', 'field_67c7d07b89280'),
(6223, 309, 'our_process_2_picon', ''),
(6224, 309, '_our_process_2_picon', 'field_67c7d09189281'),
(6225, 309, 'our_process_2_pcontent', 'Our experienced film crew brings your story to life. Using state-of-the-art equipment and creative expertise, we capture high-quality footage that aligns perfectly with the storyboard and your vision. We ensure a smooth and efficient filming process.'),
(6226, 309, '_our_process_2_pcontent', 'field_67c7d09b89282'),
(6227, 309, 'our_process_3_processname', 'Post-Production & Editing'),
(6228, 309, '_our_process_3_processname', 'field_67c7d07b89280'),
(6229, 309, 'our_process_3_picon', ''),
(6230, 309, '_our_process_3_picon', 'field_67c7d09189281'),
(6231, 309, 'our_process_3_pcontent', 'The magic happens in post-production. Our skilled editors assemble the footage, add visual effects, create motion graphics, enhance the audio, and color grade the final product. We meticulously craft every detail to create a polished and impactful video.'),
(6232, 309, '_our_process_3_pcontent', 'field_67c7d09b89282'),
(6233, 309, 'our_process_4_processname', 'Review & Refinement'),
(6234, 309, '_our_process_4_processname', 'field_67c7d07b89280'),
(6235, 309, 'our_process_4_picon', ''),
(6236, 309, '_our_process_4_picon', 'field_67c7d09189281'),
(6237, 309, 'our_process_4_pcontent', 'We value your feedback. We present you with a draft of the video and work closely with you to incorporate any revisions or refinements.  We ensure you\'re completely satisfied with the final product.'),
(6238, 309, '_our_process_4_pcontent', 'field_67c7d09b89282'),
(6239, 309, 'our_process_5_processname', 'Delivery & Distribution'),
(6240, 309, '_our_process_5_processname', 'field_67c7d07b89280'),
(6241, 309, 'our_process_5_picon', ''),
(6242, 309, '_our_process_5_picon', 'field_67c7d09189281'),
(6243, 309, 'our_process_5_pcontent', 'Once you\'re happy with the final cut, we deliver your video in the format and resolution you require. We can also assist with distribution strategies, helping you reach your target audience and maximize the impact of your video.'),
(6244, 309, '_our_process_5_pcontent', 'field_67c7d09b89282'),
