(7020, 320, '_all_service_0_all_service_images', 'field_67c69b0d1cfee'),
(7021, 320, 'all_service_1_all_service_title', '[:en]Creative Direction & Scriptwriting[:]'),
(7022, 320, '_all_service_1_all_service_title', 'field_67c69ae61cfec'),
(7023, 320, 'all_service_1_all_service_content', '[:en]The foundation of any successful film or advertisement lies in a compelling story and a clear creative vision. Nexuslinc\'s creative direction and scriptwriting services provide the essential building blocks for impactful campaigns. Our experienced creative directors collaborate with you to develop a unique and engaging concept that aligns with your brand identity and marketing objectives. From initial brainstorming and concept development to scriptwriting, storyboarding, and pre-production planning, we provide the creative leadership and compelling narratives that set your film and advertising projects apart.[:]'),
(7024, 320, '_all_service_1_all_service_content', 'field_67c69afe1cfed'),
(7025, 320, 'all_service_1_all_service_images', '[:en]329[:]'),
(7026, 320, '_all_service_1_all_service_images', 'field_67c69b0d1cfee'),
(7027, 320, 'all_service_2_all_service_title', '[:en]Post-Production Editing & Color Grading[:]'),
(7028, 320, '_all_service_2_all_service_title', 'field_67c69ae61cfec'),
(7029, 320, 'all_service_2_all_service_content', '[:en]The finishing touches are just as important as the initial creation. Nexuslinc\'s post-production editing and color grading services polish your film and advertising projects, transforming raw footage into a captivating and visually stunning final product. Our team of skilled editors utilizes industry-standard software and techniques to assemble your footage, create seamless transitions, add visual effects, and refine the pacing to maximize impact. With this, we ensure a polished and professional final product that captivates your audience.[:]'),
(7030, 320, '_all_service_2_all_service_content', 'field_67c69afe1cfed'),
(7031, 320, 'all_service_2_all_service_images', '[:en]330[:]'),
(7032, 320, '_all_service_2_all_service_images', 'field_67c69b0d1cfee'),
(7033, 320, 'all_service_3_all_service_title', '[:en]Sound Design & Original Music Scoring[:]'),
(7034, 320, '_all_service_3_all_service_title', 'field_67c69ae61cfec'),
(7035, 320, 'all_service_3_all_service_content', '[:en]Sound is more than just background noise! Nexuslinc\'s sound design and original music scoring services create an immersive auditory experience that complements your visuals and resonates with your audience. Our team of sound designers crafts intricate soundscapes, adding depth and realism to your project. From sound effects and dialogue editing to music composition and mixing, our audio services bring your project to life, creating a truly immersive and unforgettable experience for your viewers.[:]'),
(7036, 320, '_all_service_3_all_service_content', 'field_67c69afe1cfed'),
(7037, 320, 'all_service_3_all_service_images', '[:en]331[:]'),
(7038, 320, '_all_service_3_all_service_images', 'field_67c69b0d1cfee'),
(7039, 320, 'all_service_4_all_service_title', '[:en]Media Planning & Ad Placement Strategy[:]'),
(7040, 320, '_all_service_4_all_service_title', 'field_67c69ae61cfec'),
(7041, 320, 'all_service_4_all_service_content', '[:en]Creating impactful film and advertising is only half the battle; ensuring it reaches the right audience is just as crucial. Nexuslinc\'s media planning and ad placement strategy services maximize the reach and effectiveness of your campaigns. Our team of media experts analyzes your target audience, researches media consumption habits, and develops a customized media plan that aligns with your budget and marketing objectives. We handle every aspect of your media strategy and ensure your message reaches the right people at the right time.[:]'),
