(7170, 324, '_our_client_heading', 'field_67c68f97c388d'),
(7171, 324, 'our_client_content', '<p>We\'ve partnered with a diverse roster of clients, from emerging startups to established global brands, helping them connect with their target audiences through impactful film and advertising campaigns. Explore the impactful film and advertising campaigns we\'ve created for our clients.  We\'re proud to showcase the results we\'ve achieved through strategic thinking, creative innovation, and a dedication to delivering exceptional quality.</p>'),
