(11229, 451, '_all_service_1_all_service_title', 'field_67c69ae61cfec'),
(11230, 451, 'all_service_1_all_service_content', 'Enhance your brand\'s presence and engage your online audience with Nexuslinc\'s 2D animation services. We craft 2D animations tailored for branding, social media content, and web videos, ensuring your message is delivered with style and impact. From eye-catching animated logos and brand intros to engaging social media clips and informative web explainer videos, our team of 2D animators brings your ideas to life with creativity and precision.'),
