(11350, 456, 'our_client_content', '<p>We believe that great animation is born from strong partnerships. At Nexuslinc, we work closely with our clients, understanding their brand identity, target audience, and project goals. We\'ve had the privilege of collaborating with a diverse range of clients, from advertising agencies and marketing teams to educational institutions and entertainment studios. We\'re proud to have helped our clients bring their creative visions to life and achieve their communication goals.</p>'),
(11351, 456, '_our_client_content', 'field_67c693d1ac63f'),
(11352, 456, 'our_client_logo', 'a:6:{i:0;s:3:\"207\";i:1;s:3:\"205\";i:2;s:3:\"206\";i:3;s:3:\"204\";i:4;s:3:\"203\";i:5;s:3:\"202\";}'),
