(11357, 456, '_service_heading', 'field_67c699785f93a'),
(11358, 456, 'service_content', '<p>Nexuslinc offers a full spectrum of 3D and 2D animation services, transforming your ideas into visually compelling realities. From crafting dynamic 3D animations for commercials and explainer videos to creating engaging 2D animations for social media and branding, we provide a seamless and comprehensive approach. We transform your concepts into engaging animations that captivate and inspire.</P'),
